==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Oospore
<hw>O"o*spore</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>w,'o`n</grk> an egg + <?/ a seed.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A special kind of spore resulting from the
fertilization of an oosphere by antherozoids.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A
fertilized oosphere in the ovule of a flowering plant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oosporic</ent>⟦br⟧
